content: Paid $5 for a product that tells me "product is not licenced please purchase from play store". I bought the game from the play store. Refunded.

So many features do not work. Waste of money. To name a few: cannot upload photos from the camera roll, cannot play video in the app, when video is saved and played outside the app all audio is played after the book is complete, and there are too few creative options. For example, there's only one light skin character and you can't change eye or hair color etc, so when my child wanted to do a story about her and her best friends, she had to use the same character to represent all of them.
How do you add text to the speech bubble stickers?
I love this because you can make great story's 1 to 1,000 I pick 1,000
